583
00:35:32,880 --> 00:35:34,680
But take this present first.

584
00:35:35,320 --> 00:35:37,160
Actually
I’ve got another present for you.

585
00:35:37,880 --> 00:35:39,400
But I’ll wait until you get to work.

586
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:41,120
You’ll see.

587
00:35:41,800 --> 00:35:43,240
Open it. Do you like it?

588
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:50,720
This is cute.

589
00:35:54,400 --> 00:35:55,400
I’ll put it on for you.

590
00:36:05,200 --> 00:36:06,200
What are you doing?

591
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:10,680
What are you doing here?

592
00:36:11,360 --> 00:36:12,680
This is my home.

593
00:36:13,560 --> 00:36:14,840
Why can’t I come in?

594
00:36:26,160 --> 00:36:28,200
- Mom.
- Happy Birthday.

595
00:36:28,360 --> 00:36:31,080
- Surprise.
- Happy birthday to you, dear.

596
00:36:34,640 --> 00:36:35,640
Mom.

597
00:36:36,080 --> 00:36:37,920
I missed you.

598
00:36:41,080 --> 00:36:42,080
Oh.

599
00:36:43,040 --> 00:36:45,680
Isn’t this the guy in the news?

600
00:36:46,800 --> 00:36:49,960
He likes you and you like him, right?

601
00:36:50,920 --> 00:36:53,080
No, mom. Calm down first.

602
00:36:53,080 --> 00:36:56,000
He just came to give me a present, see?

603
00:37:02,040 --> 00:37:03,320
And who’s this?

604
00:37:06,520 --> 00:37:07,520
Who is it?

605
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:13,280
This is my friend. My friend.

606
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,760
But I’m not her friend.

607
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:23,680
There’re three of you here?

608
00:37:27,080 --> 00:37:29,080
It’s not like that, mom.

609
00:37:29,120 --> 00:37:31,280
My friends

610
00:37:31,280 --> 00:37:33,000
went outside to buy some stuff.

611
00:37:33,000 --> 00:37:36,520
So we three are here to set up the room.

612
00:37:36,520 --> 00:37:38,160
Yeah, right?

613
00:37:38,160 --> 00:37:41,080
Oh really? That’s good.

614
00:37:41,080 --> 00:37:44,000
I made some northern style food.
Let’s have them together.

615
00:37:44,120 --> 00:37:45,020
Please.

616
00:37:45,020 --> 00:37:47,400
Let’s have some northern style food.
Do you like northern style food?

617
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:48,280
I do, auntie.

618
00:37:48,280 --> 00:37:50,760
How are you doing lately?

619
00:37:50,760 --> 00:37:52,160
There’re still a lot of things going on.

620
00:37:52,160 --> 00:37:53,800
- That’s great.
- It’s nice meeting you.

621
00:37:53,840 --> 00:37:54,840
Me too.

622
00:37:58,920 --> 00:38:00,240
Hello, Wawa.

623
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:02,680
Happy birthday, my best friend.
I was about to call you.

624
00:38:03,400 --> 00:38:06,200
You come to my place, now.

625
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:07,720
Why?

626
00:38:08,440 --> 00:38:10,220
Just come. I’ll tell you later.

627
00:38:10,220 --> 00:38:12,700
Don’t forget to buy a few things over.

628
00:38:12,700 --> 00:38:15,360
If you don’t come,
it’ll be a big problem.

629
00:38:16,080 --> 00:38:16,920
Alright?

630
00:38:16,920 --> 00:38:18,800
Alright, okay. See you soon.

631
00:38:19,080 --> 00:38:20,160
Um.

632
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:28,200
Why are you in so much shock?

633
00:38:30,280 --> 00:38:31,440
Because of you.

634
00:38:31,440 --> 00:38:33,800
Why didn’t you tell me
you’re in Bangkok?

635
00:38:33,800 --> 00:38:35,960
Mom won’t let me tell you.

636
00:38:36,040 --> 00:38:37,960
You know I can’t argue with her.

637
00:38:39,320 --> 00:38:40,440
But

638
00:38:41,440 --> 00:38:43,720
why are you acting strange today?

639
00:38:43,960 --> 00:38:47,240
Or you have a secret to me?

640
00:38:47,240 --> 00:38:48,400
No.

641
00:38:48,400 --> 00:38:50,440
How could I have a secret to you?

642
00:38:50,440 --> 00:38:52,520
Just go back inside and help mom.

643
00:38:52,520 --> 00:38:54,400
- Why are you letting mom do it alone?
- I think you have a boyfriend.

644
00:38:54,400 --> 00:38:56,400
You’re crazy. I don’t have one.

645
00:38:56,400 --> 00:38:57,680
Let me help you.

646
00:38:57,680 --> 00:39:00,720
It’s alright, dear.
Make yourself comfortable.

647
00:39:00,720 --> 00:39:02,200
Let me help you.

648
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:04,360
- Do you want to help?
- Sure.

649
00:39:04,360 --> 00:39:05,240
Sure.

650
00:39:05,240 --> 00:39:06,280
Please excuse me.

651
00:39:06,280 --> 00:39:07,000
Sure.

652
00:39:07,760 --> 00:39:09,680
Prapai is very similar to you.

653
00:39:09,920 --> 00:39:14,280
Both sweet and beautiful.

654
00:39:15,880 --> 00:39:17,800
You’re cute too.

655
00:39:18,720 --> 00:39:20,480
But before today,

656
00:39:20,480 --> 00:39:23,840
I saw you in the news.
I thought you were going to

657
00:39:23,840 --> 00:39:26,520
do something bad to Prapai.

658
00:39:26,800 --> 00:39:30,160
These reporters are really mean.

659
00:39:30,160 --> 00:39:31,880
How can they write something like that?

660
00:39:32,080 --> 00:39:33,600
It’s alright, auntie.

661
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:36,600
At least you and Prapai
don’t misunderstand.

662
00:39:36,600 --> 00:39:38,200
I’m flattered.

663
00:39:38,200 --> 00:39:39,400
Good then.

664
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:43,200
So enjoy my northern style food today.

665
00:39:43,200 --> 00:39:46,760
Wow. I’m sure I’ll finish it all.

666
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:50,880
I’ll open it, mom.

667
00:39:50,880 --> 00:39:51,480
Sure.

668
00:39:56,080 --> 00:39:57,440
Wawa, come on in.

669
00:39:57,440 --> 00:39:58,960
So what’s going on?

670
00:40:00,920 --> 00:40:02,680
Hey, everyone.

671
00:40:02,680 --> 00:40:03,680
Hello, auntie.

672
00:40:03,680 --> 00:40:04,960
Ta.

673
00:40:04,960 --> 00:40:06,980
Come on in first, both of you.

674
00:40:07,100 --> 00:40:08,600
Come on, come on.

675
00:40:11,880 --> 00:40:14,960
Let’s help set up. Feel free to do so.

676
00:40:16,720 --> 00:40:18,000
Have a look at what you want to eat.

677
00:40:18,000 --> 00:40:19,120
What do you want?

678
00:40:19,200 --> 00:40:20,700
- Anything is fine.
- Northern chili paste?

679
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:21,800
What did you buy?

680
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,480
Here you go.

681
00:40:28,680 --> 00:40:30,280
I’ll be right back.

682
00:40:37,080 --> 00:40:38,080
- Prapai.
- Yes?

683
00:40:38,080 --> 00:40:40,600
Bring me the glasses.
I’ll set them up for you.

684
00:40:40,600 --> 00:40:42,000
Sure, mom.

685
00:40:45,840 --> 00:40:46,840
That one too.

686
00:40:48,040 --> 00:40:49,120
Thank you.

687
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:50,720
I’m coming.

