689
00:41:21,160 --> 00:41:25,400
♪Happy Birthday to you♪

690
00:41:25,440 --> 00:41:29,520
♪Happy Birthday to you♪

691
00:41:29,680 --> 00:41:31,800
♪Happy Birthday♪

