00:41:43,040 --> 00:41:44,240
Make a wish, dear.

695
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:55,800
Thank you.

696
00:41:57,800 --> 00:41:59,680
What does the cake say?

697
00:42:00,480 --> 00:42:02,560
