Let’s take a photo.

702
00:42:22,080 --> 00:42:23,320
I’ll take it for you.

703
00:42:23,440 --> 00:42:24,800
- Okay.
- Give it to me.

704
00:42:30,680 --> 00:42:33,480
Come on, one, two, three.

705
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:44,520
Hey.

706
00:42:45,120 --> 00:42:46,360
I’ll cut it for you.

707
00:42:47,800 --> 00:42:49,240
Alright, there you go.

708
00:42:49,400 --> 00:42:50,520
Be careful.

709
00:43:15,680 --> 00:43:16,800
Okay.

710
00:43:19,000 --> 00:43:20,560
I’ll do yours first, auntie.

711
00:43:20,560 --> 00:43:21,520
Sure.

712
00:43:21,840 --> 00:43:22,800
Just a moment.

713
00:43:36,320 --> 00:43:37,880
Come on, cheers.

714
00:43:40,440 --> 00:43:42,960
I’ll tell you something.
Don’t let her drink.

715
00:43:43,320 --> 00:43:44,560
Otherwise she’ll go crazy.

716
00:43:44,560 --> 00:43:46,400
Oh, mom.

717
00:43:47,400 --> 00:43:48,400
She also bites.

718
00:43:49,560 --> 00:43:50,560
Bite?

719
00:43:52,640 --> 00:43:53,920
It’s true, auntie.

720
00:43:53,920 --> 00:43:54,960
I want to complain.

721
00:43:54,960 --> 00:43:55,760
Yea?

722
00:43:55,760 --> 00:43:57,440
I met with Pai once, when she was drunk.

723
00:43:57,440 --> 00:43:59,600
She was walking around,

724
00:43:59,600 --> 00:44:01,400
and just bit my arm. Just like this.

725
00:44:01,400 --> 00:44:02,800
Her teeth are very sharp.

726
00:44:03,480 --> 00:44:05,360
I experienced it too.

727
00:44:05,360 --> 00:44:08,640
I told you I was dreaming about
having pork leg back then.

728
00:44:08,640 --> 00:44:10,720
But it’s your friend’s arm.

729
00:44:10,720 --> 00:44:14,520
See? I told you.
Once she drinks, she goes crazy.

730
00:44:14,520 --> 00:44:16,480
Mom.

731
00:44:16,520 --> 00:44:17,960
So then let’s give it to me.

732
00:44:17,960 --> 00:44:20,360
- No. Not for you.
- Stop right there.

733
00:44:21,120 --> 00:44:22,480
But today is your birthday,
you can have some.

734
00:44:22,480 --> 00:44:24,400
- Yay. Cheers.
- Yay.

735
00:44:29,040 --> 00:44:30,080
Here.

736
00:44:30,080 --> 00:44:31,200
Thank you.

737
00:44:31,720 --> 00:44:35,080
Mom, you and Peng can go back first.

738
00:44:35,080 --> 00:44:36,800
Me and my friends
will finish off the rest.

739
00:44:36,800 --> 00:44:39,760
How can you let your visitors
clean up the room?

740
00:44:39,800 --> 00:44:41,120
You’re the owner of the room.

741
00:44:41,120 --> 00:44:44,520
Kids, you can all go back.
Aren’t you all working tomorrow?

742
00:44:44,520 --> 00:44:46,240
I’ll finish off everything.

743
00:44:47,320 --> 00:44:49,120
- So then I’ll have to excuse myself.
- Sure.

744
00:44:49,120 --> 00:44:50,240
- Bye.
- Bye.

745
00:44:50,240 --> 00:44:51,920
You still have something to tell me.

746
00:44:51,920 --> 00:44:53,000
I know. We’ll talk later.

747
00:44:53,000 --> 00:44:54,840
- Alright, see you.
- Bye.

748
00:45:06,120 --> 00:45:08,120
I’ll head out too. See you.

749
00:45:08,120 --> 00:45:09,920
- See you.
- I’m going now, auntie.

750
00:45:09,920 --> 00:45:11,720
- Sure. See you later.
- Sure, mom.

751
00:45:12,000 --> 00:45:13,440
Don’t forget to go back home
to Chiang Mai too.

752
00:45:13,440 --> 00:45:14,320
Sure.

753
00:45:14,760 --> 00:45:15,640
See you later, Peng.

754
00:45:15,640 --> 00:45:16,920
Bye, Ta.

755
00:45:19,000 --> 00:45:22,120
Oh, how about you?
Aren’t you going back?

756
00:45:22,880 --> 00:45:24,560
You’re not the owner.

757
00:45:24,560 --> 00:45:27,160
Let the owner do it herself. You can go.

758
00:45:33,360 --> 00:45:34,440
Prapai.

759
00:45:34,440 --> 00:45:35,080
Yeah?

760
00:45:35,120 --> 00:45:36,120
I’m going to go now.

761
00:45:37,080 --> 00:45:40,600
Auntie, if I have the chance.
I’ll go visit you at Chiang Mai.

762
00:45:40,600 --> 00:45:42,320
Sure. You’re very welcome.

763
00:45:42,320 --> 00:45:44,080
I’ll leave now. Bye.

764
00:45:44,080 --> 00:45:45,280
Good luck.

765
00:45:45,840 --> 00:45:47,360
- See you later.
- See you.

766
00:45:58,200 --> 00:45:59,440
I’ll head out now.

767
00:45:59,440 --> 00:46:00,720
Good luck.

768
00:46:01,600 --> 00:46:02,920
Bye.

769
00:46:13,600 --> 00:46:15,120
I’ll wash it later.

770
00:46:27,680 --> 00:46:29,040
Hop on, I’ll drop you off.

771
00:46:30,600 --> 00:46:33,160
It’s alright. I’ll find a taxi.

772
00:46:44,840 --> 00:46:46,120
Come on, get in the car.

773
00:46:47,320 --> 00:46:48,400
Quickly.

774
00:46:49,000 --> 00:46:51,240
It’s getting dark soon.
It’s going to be dangerous.

775
00:46:51,400 --> 00:46:52,880
It’s dangerous going alone.

776
00:46:53,960 --> 00:46:55,480
I’ll drop you as a friend.

777
00:47:21,880 --> 00:47:23,080
Take care of yourself.

778
00:47:23,080 --> 00:47:24,280
Yes, mom.

779
00:47:24,840 --> 00:47:26,400
You know,

780
00:47:26,400 --> 00:47:28,440
if Peng doesn’t have school tomorrow,

781
00:47:28,440 --> 00:47:30,440
I would want to stay the night.

782
00:47:30,440 --> 00:47:31,880
I missed you so much.

783
00:47:31,880 --> 00:47:33,200
Mom.

784
00:47:33,200 --> 00:47:37,280
I missed you too, mom.
I want you to stay too.

785
00:47:37,280 --> 00:47:38,860
But if you don’t leave now,

786
00:47:38,860 --> 00:47:39,920
you’re going to miss the flight.

787
00:47:39,920 --> 00:47:41,920
You can just send me here.

788
00:47:41,920 --> 00:47:43,120
Sure.

789
00:47:43,120 --> 00:47:45,800
Peng, take care of mom.

790
00:47:45,920 --> 00:47:47,800
Okay, noted.

791
00:47:47,800 --> 00:47:48,400
Good job.

792
00:47:48,400 --> 00:47:50,080
- You take care of yourself too.
- Sure.

793
00:47:50,080 --> 00:47:52,320
- Give me a hug. I missed you.
- Sure.

794
00:47:52,320 --> 00:47:53,840
- Come back to Chiang Mai too.
- Yes, mom.

795
00:47:55,440 --> 00:47:57,280
- Bye mom.
- Bye, Pai.

796
00:47:57,280 --> 00:47:59,040
- Bye. See you.
- See you next time.

797
00:47:59,520 --> 00:48:01,080
- Bye.
- Bye.

798
00:48:12,960 --> 00:48:14,000
Thank you.

799
00:48:14,000 --> 00:48:16,520
Next time if you need a ride,
you can tell me.

800
00:48:17,280 --> 00:48:20,440
Why?
Did you change your job to a driver?

801
00:48:21,720 --> 00:48:24,880
If you want me to be a driver, I can be.

802
00:48:25,080 --> 00:48:27,040
But I have to tell you,
this car is special.

803
00:48:27,440 --> 00:48:29,480
Because this car will take only you.

804
00:48:31,760 --> 00:48:33,320
No, thank you.

805
00:48:33,720 --> 00:48:35,160
I don’t want to disturb you.

806
00:48:35,640 --> 00:48:36,880
I can go on my own.

807
00:48:37,600 --> 00:48:39,600
I used to travel alone anyway.

808
00:49:03,600 --> 00:49:04,720
Pupaa.

809
00:49:24,200 --> 00:49:26,840
Pupaa. I’m sorry.

810
00:49:26,840 --> 00:49:29,000
I was having a long talk with my mom.

